{"id":81373,"title":"Treatment of a unilateral class II malocclusion with Sabbagh Universal Spring: a case report.","abstract":"Unilateral class II malocclusion is a treatment challenge. Several treatment approaches have been recommended; each with particular limitations. Fixed functional appliances are quite popular because of invisibility, minimal interference with speech, and not relying on patient cooperation. This article describes a clinical case treated satisfactorily using unilateral Sabbagh Universal Spring.","date":"2014-08-11","categories":"Stomatognathic Diseases","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25109052","annotations":[{"name":"Patient","weight":0.258263,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Patient"},{"name":"Therapy","weight":0.20625,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Therapy"},{"name":"Cooperation","weight":0.0370044,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cooperation"},{"name":"Malocclusion","weight":0.0297972,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Malocclusion"},{"name":"Speech","weight":0.0279596,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Speech"},{"name":"Major histocompatibility complex","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Major_histocompatibility_complex"},{"name":"Clinical trial","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Clinical_trial"},{"name":"Unilateralism","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Unilateralism"},{"name":"Electromagnetic interference","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Electromagnetic_interference"},{"name":"Case report","weight":0.0148276,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Case_report"},{"name":"Social class","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Social_class"},{"name":"Invisibility","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Invisibility"},{"name":"Home appliance","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Home_appliance"},{"name":"Autism therapies","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Autism_therapies"}]}
